{
  "texts": [
    "Later stages of training incorporated QLoRA with four-bit quantization and an adapter rank of 16.",
    "The fine-tuning process was carried out with 107 curated requirements lists, completed over nine epochs.",
    "Training was marked by smooth transitions and incremental improvements, ensuring consistency in the outputs.",
    "The model achieved a validation loss value of 0.4332, which was smoothed to 0.4419 after 350 steps.",
    "Notably, the threshold for an acceptable validation loss (< 1) was already reached after processing 75 lists, adhering to the characteristics of requirements according to ISO 29148 (2018)."
  ]
}